[0-9]	(0-9) To change channel.
 [SOURCE]	(A) To display the input source list.
 [TIMER]	(B) To display the time.
 [SLEEP]	(C) To set the sleep time.
 [ZOOM]	(D) To select the zoom.
 [PEFFECT]	(E) To select the screen effect.
 [SEFFECT]	(F) To select the sound effect.
 [ASPECT]	(G) To change the aspect ratio.
 [CHUP]	(O) To turn up the channel.
 [CHDN]	(Q) To turn down the channel.
 [MUTE]	(R) To mute or un-mute the sound.
 [VOLUME_UP]	(M) To turn up the volume.
 [VOLUME_DOWN]	(N) To turn down the volume.
 [DPAD_CENTER]	 (ENTER) To display the channel list.
 [INFO]	(S) To display the channel info.
 [EJECT]	(U) To display the channel info.
 [PLAYPAUSE]	(V) To display the favorite list.
 [YELLOW]	(K) To select the type of the channel list.
